### ⚙️ API Configuration
→ **AUTO-FILLED by `[API: ...]` tag** when you paste the Master Prompt

When you paste any Master Prompt into a PromptNode or CarouselPromptNode, the `[API: ...]` tag on line 1 is detected within 500ms. The app parses all values, applies them to the node settings panel instantly, then strips the tag before sending to Gemini. You will see:

`⚡ Auto-filled: temperature, topP, topK, seed, model`

The settings sliders and inputs update in real time — no manual entry needed.

**Model tag → app selector mapping:**

| Tag value | App model selector |
|---|---|
| `gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview` | Flash |
| `gemini-3-pro-image-preview` | Pro |
| `gemini-2.5-flash-image` | Standard |
| anything containing `pro` | Pro |
| anything containing `standard` | Standard |
| anything else | Flash |

**Manual fallback:** The Paste API Config box in the right sidebar still accepts the old JSON format as a manual override. Scene-keyword presets (beach, studio, urban) fire as lowest priority if no tag and no manual entry is found.

**Note on candidateCount:** The app generates 1 image per OutputNode. `candidateCount` is not used — use the Seed Explorer instead.

